ny focuses on providing proportional reinsurance to small single state and regional carriers the companys general liability insurance policies are issued to business organizations to protect them against liability claims for bodily injury and property damage arising out of premises operations products and completed operations and advertising and personal injury liability the companys professional liability is a form of liability insurance that helps protect professional advisors and serviceproviding individuals and companies from bearing the full cost of defending against a negligence claim made by a client and damages awarded in a civil lawsuit the companys credit and financial lines primarily consist of mortgage insurance policies it focuses on private mortgage insurance pmi in addition to mortgage insurance policies classified as credit and financial lines include political risk trade credit surety financial guarantee residual value insurance and title insurance the company provides multiline reinsurance which is reinsurance of an underlying portfolio of various different types of insurance risks extended warranty insurance is included in multiline business extended warranty insurance compensates individuals or businesses for correction or repair necessary as a result of mechanical or electrical breakdown the companys extended warranty insurance business it writes excludes manufacturer defect and product recall extended warranty insurance covers a range of units such as motor vehicles vans trucks construction equipment and agricultural equipment the company also offers professional liability insurancethe company competes with alleghany corporation arch capital group ltd axis capital holdings ltd chubb limited endurance specialty holdings ltd everest re group ltd greenlight reinsurance ltd hamilton insurance group ltd hannover ruckversicherung ag maiden holdings ltd munchener ruckversicherungsgesellschaft ag partnerre ltd swiss re limited tokio marine holdings inc